data.description: Qualifying assumable 3.375% FHA loan. This lovely one store home on a quarter acre lot with an in ground pool and storage shed is ready for a new owner. Three bedroom and two full bathrooms with upgraded bathroom plumbing fixtures. Tile flooring in all but one room. A spacious eat-in kitchen with granite tile counters and a Bosch dishwasher, overlooks the large backyard. A large covered back patio is perfect for al fresco dining or morning coffee. The pool pump was new in 2021. Also in the large backyard is a storage shed and fenced dog run. The attached two car garage features a garage door opener and washer/dryer hookups. Close to the medical center, shopping and restaurants.
